  "prompt": "What are some of the cool features on Google now?",
  "response": "Here are some cool features of Google Now (now part of Google Assistant):\n\n1. Voice Search\n- Hands-free voice commands\n- Natural language processing\n- Ability to ask complex questions\n\n2. Personalized Information Cards\n- Weather updates\n- Traffic and commute information\n- Flight and travel details\n- Sports scores and schedules\n- Nearby restaurant recommendations\n\n3. Location-Based Suggestions\n- Nearby attractions\n- Local events\n- Restaurants and points of interest\n- Public transit information\n\n4. Context-Aware Reminders\n- Location-based reminders\n- Time-based reminders\n- Integrates with calendar and contacts\n\n5. Language Translation\n- Real-time translation\n- Supports multiple languages\n- Text and voice translation\n\n6. Personal Assistant Functions\n- Setting alarms\n- Creating calendar events\n- Making calls\n- Sending messages\n- Controlling smart home devices\n\n7. Information Anticipation\n- Predicts information you might need\n- learns from your search history and behaviors\n- Provides proactive suggestions\n\n8. Integration with Other Google Services\n- Gmail\n- Google Maps\n- Google Calendar\n- Google Drive\n\nNote: Some features might vary depending on your device and Google Assistant version.",
